      "span_text": "Second, to use data from the GENetic and clinical Predictors Of treatment response in Depression (GENPOD) trial (Lewis et al. 2011; [CITATION_1] to illustrate how to adjust for differential non-adherence in an RCT of two active interventions and hence to derive an unbiased estimate of the efficacy of reboxetine compared with citalopram in the treatment of primary care patients with a new episode of depression.",
